      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$20,000 - Embrace the journey with a car that\u2019s ready for more adventures! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition, showing some character from its time on the road but still delivering a dependable and steady drive. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver with a great history at an accessible price point!",
