    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a respectable shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some light surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with the upholstery showing only minor wear from regular use. All major mechanical systems are functioning properly, and the car drives smoothly. It is a reliable choice for someone looking for a well-maintained vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
