    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW M240i Coupe is a refined enthusiast's machine, finished in classic Alpine White over a Black Dakota leather interior. Under the hood, the 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six runs flawlessly, delivering linear power through a crisp 8-speed sport automatic transmission. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear quarter panel. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the heated leather seats show minimal bolster wear, and all electronics\u2014including the iDrive navigation and Harman Kardon sound system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is current on all scheduled maintenance, recently receiving a fresh oil service and a new set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The 18-inch M-Double Spoke wheels are in excellent shape with no curb rash. This is a reliable, spirited daily driver that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
